kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.linked_lists

Class LinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.linked_lists.ListAdapter<T>
      • kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.linked_lists.LinkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type parameter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>

    public class LinkedList<T>
extends ListAdapter<T>
     An implementation of a Linked List. A Linked List is similar to an array structure as it
 keeps track of a list of items, but instead of using an array, it uses a series of nodes
 to store all its items.
    See Also:
    Linked List
    Date:
    Fall 2012
